### Registro de usuario

POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/registro
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Iván García",
  "email": "ivan@test.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "username": "ivangarcia"
}

### Registro con email duplicado (debe fallar)

POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/registro
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Otro Iván",
  "email": "ivan@test.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "username": "otrouser"
}

### Login correcto

POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "ivan@test.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### Login con contraseña incorrecta (debe fallar)

POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "ivan@test.com",
  "password": "incorrecta"
}

### Verificar token (sin token, debe fallar)

GET http://localhost:3001/api/auth/verificar

### Verificar token (con token correcto)

GET http://localhost:3001/api/auth/verificar
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6IjY5Zjg0ZDU1MjM0MmUwZTZlMDc4ZGZlNCIsInJvbCI6InVzdWFyaW8iLCJpYXQiOjE3Nzg3NDM4MzMsImV4cCI6MTc3OTM0ODYzM30.LACXrGQj30KO95kvD-zWnPRRDMWCdy11lmpuj3wr1Gs
